<BlogArticleLayout
  title="Peptides for Anti-Aging: GH Secretagogues, NAD+, and the Longevity Axis"
  seoTitle="Peptides for Anti-Aging: The Evidence"
  subtitle="Aging isn't one process — it's the measurable decline of specific systems like the growth-hormone axis and NAD+ metabolism. Here's what physician-supervised peptide therapy can and can't realistically do about it."
